data.description: Gorgeous 1.5 story custom home in Cedar Creek’s Shadow Highlands is a dream waiting to become your new home. The stunning entryway is only a glimpse into what this beautiful house has to offer. While the master suite is conveniently located on the main floor, the other, very spacious, bedrooms are privately tucked away upstairs. The Darling Master Bath is completed with granite countertops, while marble dazzles in the main level hall bathroom. The Kitchen dazzles with a Super Sized Island, Loads Of Cabinetry and Stunning White Marble counter-tops. And you won’t want to miss the year-round sunroom that sits just off the patio, overlooking the beautiful yard. From the high ceilings to the rich wood floors this home is nothing but grand. Located in Cedar Creek, offering a one of a kind lifestyle to its residents through the award winning golf course, multiple clubhouses, pools, lakes, walking trails, and upscale amenities. The swim and racquet club was recently redone and is super modern and beautiful There will also be a new pool (3rd) being built by next summer in the neighborhood.
